<title>PERU: Italian priest killed by bandits in Peru.</title>
<headline>Italian priest killed by bandits in Peru.</headline>
<dateline>LIMA 1997-03-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bandits in northern Peru have abducted and killed an Italian priest, the Italian embassy in Lima said on Wednesday.</p>
<p>The priest, identified only as Father Badiali, was killed by robbers over the weekend near the village of Huari, in Ancash department about 320 miles (400 km) north of Lima, said an embassy spokesman.</p>
<p>No further details were immediately available.</p>
